// in the command line
1)go to perticular folder where you want to download
// in the web page
2)get the url of the git page
// it will download to (step 1) perticular folder (your desire folder)
3)git clone https://github.com/Subbu-B/Learning_Subjets.git 

// code file in the folder 
4)now you  can modify code and save it.

// in the command line
// check the status
5) git status (if the file is not uploaded to git then it show in the red color)
// add the file to git hub web page.
6)git add file_name (like grocery.html)
// commit the file and add comments also.
7)git commit -m "comment here"
// push the code after commit
8) git push 

